<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3471082371880025"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  <script async custom-element="amp-auto-ads"
        src="https://cdn.ampproject.org/v0/amp-auto-ads-0.1.js">
  </script>

  <meta name="description" content="مكتبة طيبة المحبين وروضة المحبوبين - مكتبة معرفية تهتم بنشر العلوم النبوية والكتب الإسلامية المختارة.">
  <title>مكتبة طيبة المحبين وروضة المحبوبين</title>

  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif; margin: 0; background-color: #e9f7ef; color: #1b4332; line-height: 1.6; }
    header { background-color: #2d6a4f; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 10px 0; position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 1000; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    header img { height: 70px; width: auto; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; }
    main { padding-top: 140px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; padding-bottom: 50px; }
    
    .books-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; padding: 20px; }
    .book-item { background: #fff; border-right: 5px solid #2d6a4f; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); display: flex; align-items: center; transition: 0.3s; }
    .book-item:hover { transform: scale(1.02); background-color: #f1f8f5; }
    .book-item a { text-decoration: none; color: #1b4332; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .pdf-icon { color: #d62828; font-size: 14px; background: #f8d7da; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 5px; }

    footer { text-align: center; background-color: #2d6a4f; color: white; padding: 15px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .social a { color: white; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <amp-auto-ads type="adsense" data-ad-client="ca-pub-3471082371880025"></amp-auto-ads>

  <header>
